trump order turns federal land at us border into military installation
the u . s . military will take control of a strip of federal land that spans three states along the southern border in an effort to stem illegal immigration , a memorandum friday by donald trumpsaid .
the memorandum , " military mission forsealing the southern borderof the united states and repelling invasions , " directs the secretaries of defense , interior , agriculture and homeland security " to provide for the use and jurisdiction by the department of defense over federal lands , including the roosevelt reservation and excluding federal indian reservations , that are reasonably necessary to enable military activities . "
he wrote it could include " border - barrier construction and emplacement of detection and monitoring equipment . "
